{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"45fb2f359a","title":"毛泽东关于转发西南军区剿匪简报第四号的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4fedb7224","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":16,"articleId":"45fb2f359a"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a7ffbadf8","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于转发西南军区剿匪简报第四号的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a"},{"id":"661e8e4706","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a"},{"id":"a8b9cb0791","type":"appellation","text":"华南分局及广东军区，广西省委及广西军区并告邓谭赵：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a"},{"id":"02e092a31c","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将西南军区剿匪简报第四号转发给你们作参考。西南军区对于剿匪工作极为认真，剿匪中执行的各项政策亦是正确的，故取得了很大成绩。广西解放在西南之前而剿匪成绩则落在西南之后，为什么这样，请你们加以检讨并以结果告诉我们。我提议广西军区从十二月份起仿照西南办法每月发一次剿匪通报，总结战绩，纠正缺点，务使全省匪患在几个月内基本解决。如何，盼复。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a"},{"id":"944ef6a19e","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十一月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a"}],"page":{"id":"9584c691fc","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"45fb2f359a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}